{"tid":714451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【世界盃】球迷半場一齊去廁所 東京爆發「供水危機」","createTime":"2018-06-23T16:48:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T07:52:37.000Z","uid":22675,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f8a693259138d34c088757cd0edfaaace1351a2c","tid":714451,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T16:48:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180623/large/1529758377_d6d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180623%2Flarge%2F1529758377_d6d5.jpg&h=ade9b2c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本東京水務局周五表示，當地竟然爆發「供水危機」，而罪魁禍首竟然是正在俄羅斯參加世界盃決賽周的國家足球隊。因為球迷為了安坐電視機前支持球隊，在比賽途中都不願去廁所，直至半場休息，過百萬球迷便一窩蜂湧去廁所，因而令用水量一下子激增。<br />\n<br />\n水務局官員指出，日本擊敗哥倫比亞的比賽半場休息期間，東京市內的用水量突然一下子急升百分之二十四，「我們認為因為許多在比賽途中不上廁所，然後（半場休息時）全部一齊如廁。」<br />\n官員指出另一個用水量急升時刻則是比賽結束後一刻，估計大家忍耐了45分鐘，自然又要立即到廁所解決，用水量更急升百分之五十。<br />\n日本周日將出戰第二場分組賽對壘塞內加爾，水務局已為穩定供水作好準備。<br />\n法新社  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180623/58350431\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180623%2F58350431&d=R8DfwAJf%2FxfFw73utoIH7v7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=deabda0c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180623%2F58350431&h=6f047a84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180623/58350431</a>"},{"pid":"09d3cd509f9664e895a3f456743c24a457ee62dc","tid":714451,"uid":22349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T16:53:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"371cd9c67c10a0f7b1a018d473a6ae3315ee298d","tid":714451,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T16:55:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/as